casebody.data:
No. 11-359. Miracle Star Women’s Recovering Community, Inc., Petitioner v. Katherine Jett, et al. 565 U.S. 1046, 132 S. Ct. 589,

181 L. Ed. 2d 442,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8103, November 14, 2011.

Motion of National Association for the Advancement of Colored People, Antelope Valley Branch Unit #1023 for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certio-rari to the Court of Appeal of California, Second Appellate District, denied.
